description: In 1982 we crossed Sahara in two Land Rovers - first North to South from Tunis to Togo via Tamarasset in Algeria, and Agadez in Niger - and then back via Ouagadougou in Bourkina Fasso over Timbuktu through the Tanezrouft desert finally to Tunis. This skill provides some facts from that journey
